Package: ncappc
Title: NCA Calculations and Population Model Diagnosis
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Chayan", "Acharya", role = "aut"),
             person("Andrew C.", "Hooker", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "andrew.hooker@farmbio.uu.se"),
             person("Gulbeyaz Y.", "Turkyilmaz", role = "aut"),
             person("Siv", "Jonsson", role = "aut"),
             person("Mats O.", "Karlsson", role = "aut"))
Description: A flexible tool that can perform
    (i) traditional non-compartmental analysis (NCA) and
    (ii) Simulation-based posterior predictive checks for population
    pharmacokinetic (PK) and/or pharmacodynamic (PKPD) models using NCA metrics. 
    The methods are described in Acharya et al. (2016) <doi:10.1016/j.cmpb.2016.01.013>.
